"CHA as a landlord can't solve this problem by itself," he sighed. 
As for <PERSON>Mr. Gardner</PERSON>, at the end of our meeting he said that he was leaving the agency the following week to run for a seat on the commission that oversees the city's sewage disposal. 

   Some compare <PERSON>Henry Horner</PERSON> and other such communities with war zones like <LOCATION>Beirut</LOCATION> and <LOCATION>Northern Ireland</LOCATION>. 
